	<p style="htitle">Potteries</p>
	<p style="hp">Potteries use ore, coal and labor to make goods. They do not have to be connected to transport but they do, of course, have to be within range of a market with ore, coal and labor and be able to receive goods.</p>
	<p style="hp">You can tell when potteries are working by the kilns producing smoke.</p>

